    "192112bdd9ee19951c715b1bd61c693d8dab4f3df21ac6d09ae3eac6d2fe7c9d": "Here you go, [?], good as new.",
    "3ea87a220a98820f8bd2254ff4bbb199c05bae3d5fd2777287f7127f30c05def": "Here's your axe, [?]. It looks like there's some damage to the hilt as well, probably some missing sapphires. But I'm sure you can take care of that yourself.",
    "743b6979832e2e3b87288e1a6df7cbd78e9dc9c6df2bb42def1f2c291da53a1f": "Thank you for bringing me this news [?]. I'll need to make some time to see the city with my own eyes.",
    "90d5bbf2232c6bc1345039fbac9e14d4e91bb084e864ba5ca7d041f39da3ac6e": "I very much doubt that [?]. I'm the last Imcando dwarf left in Gielinor.",
    "c2b00e2414597d7a9938cc50746b6adb5c9934abfd3268e371a9ff362a180cd0": "You make excellent redberry pies, [?], so how can I refuse? Let me see what's wrong with it then."
